&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is where design meets performance.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re seeking an exceptional &lt;strong&gt;Lead Editor&lt;/strong&gt; to join our creative leadership team. In this pivotal role, you&#39;ll drive visual innovation across client accounts, elevating storytelling that delivers measurable performance through your creative vision, technical expertise, and leadership capabilities. As the creative cornerstone of your pod, you&#39;ll directly impact client success by shaping campaign direction and establishing creative standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead Editors bridge the gap between strategic objectives and visual execution, transforming marketing concepts into high-performing creative assets. You&#39;ll define the visual identity for clients while fostering a culture of creative excellence and operational efficiency within your team. You&#39;ll work closely with Post-Production Supervisors on team performance strategies and your own leadership development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;About TubeScience:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
